    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "`ClientPersistentKeepalive` - 客户端配置的 PersistentKeepalive"
  },
  {
    "row": 103,
    "rowsha": "QLBIlZJaqx8Hf7wF/Vo4nJLOVPfCdQVAwQLtQYH0gUQ=",
    "originContent": "`ClientPersistentKeepalive` - PersistentKeepalive for client config ",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 104,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "`MTU` - 服务器和客户端的 MTU（0 — 由 WireGuard 选择）"
