  {
    "row": 105,
    "rowsha": "jJ8pqTdZnPjXR0amJ512FeiTI2s+LaEQVsJu323XVX4=",
    "originContent": "`MTU` - MTU for the server and client (0 — make WireGuard choose)",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 106,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "#### 客户端配置 (nnnn-%client%.toml)"
  },
  {
    "row": 107,
    "rowsha": "q3/ZNhd3UT2ZIFuYq92bIjbMMTm8xMXaA9jX2Yq+8FM=",
    "originContent": "#### client configuration (nnnn-%client%.toml)",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 108,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "`ClientRoute` - 完全覆盖服务器配置中的 `ClientRoute`"
  },
  {
    "row": 109,
    "rowsha": "CgdRRDquPWyZPxo7rpp0BcTibBz3uAxs0FSrdv2Rm6Q=",
    "originContent": "`ClientRoute` - completely overrides the `ClientRoute` from the server config",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 110,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "`AddServerRoute` - 在服务器端为客户端的 AllowedIPs 添加额外网络（当您想通过服务器将一个客户端的流量路由到另一个客户端的网络时非常有用）"
  },
  {
    "row": 111,
    "rowsha": "W7p08bcbHCIYWGnfJJRnsumqgFD/a9x+HN8zv53INlg=",
    "originContent": "`AddServerRoute` - adds additional network to AllowedIPs for the client on the server side (useful ",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 112,
    "rowsha": "Ng5oNMHpJsscFmJjiJrhkguFWkA1vCGJ/GUOk71Kzno=",
    "originContent": "when you want to route traffic to one client to another client's network through the server)",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 113,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "`MTU` - 为此客户端覆盖服务器的MTU值。设置为-1以从此WireGuard客户端配置中省略MTU。"
  },
  {
    "row": 114,
    "rowsha": "0YhrTPjrD5JJ1IYpZJ1CC5LkkIkYS0QADzig+3EICiE=",
    "originContent": "`MTU` - Override server MTU with a different value for this client. Set to -1 to omit MTU from this WireGuard client config.",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 115,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "`DNS` - 覆盖服务器的`ClientDNS`设置，适用于所有客户端。指定以逗号分隔的IP列表。  "
  },
  {
    "row": 116,
    "rowsha": "G/uEE230B+u96amOvj7vSlHzdJC+LlvLHtMZ+RAZ6dY=",
    "originContent": "`DNS` - Override server `ClientDNS` setting for all clients. Specify a comma separated IP list. ",
    "translatedContent": "设置为`no`或`none`以从此WireGuard客户端配置中省略DNS。"
  },
  {
    "row": 117,
    "rowsha": "PqI7V2iQgCXc0gPoB7fnKf42Bo6I95Oa4rwj9YCkssU=",
    "originContent": "Set to `no` or `none` to omit DNS from this WireGuard client config.",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 118,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "客户端配置文件包含`PrivateKey`字段。  "
  },
  {
    "row": 119,
    "rowsha": "iaJ2Qtcv+mPse/kVVV/dyXC/m+5i+Udigucm6E/4+Gk=",
    "originContent": "Client configuration files contain `PrivateKey` field. ",
