    "row": 121,
    "rowsha": "D4P5PB0dBZRJqxxVpVtGRa9GQ/Sjw5z79g0U9h8kjeQ=",
    "originContent": "configuration (or QR code) to the client.",
    "translatedContent": "### 除Linux外的其他操作系统"
  },
  {
    "row": 122,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
