  {
    "row": 128,
    "rowsha": "hRs7RshHLRvuNrjsH9peGJSM2D0QbBmFC7gObqCnYf4=",
    "originContent": "- You will need to compile binary yourself.",
    "translatedContent": "- 编辑0001-server.toml，在PostUp4/PostUp6/PostDown4/PostDown6字段中设置您的操作系统命令。  "
  },
  {
    "row": 129,
    "rowsha": "CZjCSuWVQ6/byCsq3AqicFM3ZxT9udSBBAxe56Jdls0=",
    "originContent": "- Set the environment variable `WG_CMD_NO_DEPS` to 1 to disable any Linux-specific checks on start. ",
    "translatedContent": "- 您需要重新加载WireGuard配置：更改时手动操作，  "
  },
  {
    "row": 130,
    "rowsha": "ouVWeBeKcX8SojvlB7Psot6+uujJk2Yue/FiVuDn40Q=",
    "originContent": "- Edit 0001-server.toml and set your OS commands in PostUp4/PostUp6/PostDown4/PostDown6 fields.",
    "translatedContent": "或监视/etc/wireguard/wg*.conf文件的更改并自动重新加载WireGuard。"
  },
  {
    "row": 131,
    "rowsha": "tg19xo19Xdc39XTSLqr7pD4qG436/qDUJuBNbBpqnO0=",
    "originContent": "- You will need to reload WireGuard configuration: manually when you change something",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 132,
    "rowsha": "ikAccaV40OU/wqcZIbLyCF5E1RwdIf3QlsST7+9mZgw=",
    "originContent": "or monitor /etc/wireguard/wg*.conf files for changes and reload WireGuard automatically.",
    "translatedContent": "欢迎提交PR以添加对其他操作系统的支持。"
  },
  {
    "row": 133,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
