    "rowsha": "rjZkqeZv1I4Lj3xD4izlOghfdvROUHu4khgvYKMMm54=",
    "originContent": "### Running in Docker ",
    "translatedContent": "虽然可以，但不建议在Docker中运行WG Commander。"
  },
